@bizarro12345  When are you planning to implement this new pricing structure?  

I don’t see why someone with vm access would need core, this all in one package is suited for a smaller audience in my opinion.  As a customer I don’t like having me choice limited, but maybe good for business, maybe not. Something you have to test I guess. 

I appreciate the 7 days subscription option - letting new users testing out the product to ensure it works on their machine. I hope you keep this option open to attract new customers.
